* SQL Warehouses
** Serverless
***_ 2-6 seconds startup
***_ Intelligent Workload Management
***_ Dynamic scaling
***_ Photon + Predictive IO
***_ Best for most SQL workloads
** Pro
***_ ~4 min startup
***_ Photon + Predictive IO
***_ Custom networking/federation
***_ No Intelligent Workload Mgmt
** Classic
***_ ~4 min startup
***_ Basic Photon only
***_ Entry-level SQL performance
***_ When serverless/pro unavailable
** All types optimize for
***_ SQL execution patterns
***_ BI dashboards
***_ ETL jobs
***_ Ad hoc analysis
@endmindmap
